- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training models to predict emotion intensity. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a less likely category, but the paper does touch on the societal implications of sentiment analysis in social media. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a less likely category, but the paper does mention the use of audio features in some of their models.
